# AI Prompt Template Isolation

All LLM prompt templates live in markdown under ai/prompts/, never inline in code—facilitates versioning & review.

## Path Pattern
ai/prompts/**/*.md

## Implementation Guidelines
- Store all AI prompt templates as markdown files
- Organize by domain/feature in subdirectories
- Include metadata like version, author, and purpose as frontmatter
- Reference prompt files from code rather than hardcoding prompts
- Use variables in templates with clear placeholders (e.g., {{variable_name}})

## Example Structure
```
ai/prompts/
  ├── chat/
  │   ├── initial-greeting.md
  │   ├── help-response.md
  ├── content/
  │   ├── blog-post-generator.md
  │   ├── product-description.md
  ├── analysis/
  │   ├── sentiment-analysis.md
  │   ├── content-moderation.md
```

